@startuml CarrySprintSoftwareArchitecture

title CarrySprint Software Component Architecture

skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center

component "Browser Client" as browser
component "API Gateway Component\n(HTTP Endpoint / Router / Middleware)" as api
package "Application Component" as app {
  component "Controller" as controller
  component "Model" as model
  component "View" as view
}
database "SQLite\n(project_{id}.sqlite)" as sqlite

browser --0)-- api : HTTP API
api --0)-- controller : ZeroMQ IPC
controller --> model : Invoke domain logic
controller --> view : Build response
sqlite --0)-- model : Data Store Interface

note right of api
  Requirement-level component.
  Internal classes are out of scope.
end note

note right of app
  Performs task selection and carry-over logic.
end note

@enduml
